data.description: Welcome to residential luxury in Lemoore a remarkable two-story residence nestled on a lush golf course with its own stunning pool. This property has been expertly constructed and is presented in immaculate condition, ensuring you are captivated from the moment you enter. The front yard boasts low-maintenance artificial grass alongside a charming water fountain and a cozy patio area, accentuated by oversized French doors that create an inviting entrance. Step inside to discover a home that radiates warmth and elegance. The floors are adorned with tiles, and the grand vaulted ceilings amplify the spaciousness of the living areas. A striking staircase leads to the upper level, setting a luxurious tone right from the foyer. The living room is bathed in natural light, offering a serene space that is both spacious and welcoming. Adjacent to it is a versatile formal dining room or flex space, seamlessly connected to the main living area. The heart of the home is the kitchen, a culinary haven with rich wooden cabinets and dark granite countertops, complemented by a breakfast bar for casual dining. Slide open the patio doors and step out to your private oasis, where a sparkling pool and breathtaking views of the golf course await. Upstairs, the allure continues with two well-appointed bedrooms and a full bathroom for guests. The owner's suite is a masterpiece of design, featuring a vast bathroom with an oval soaking tub, a stand-alone shower, and dual vanities. Attached to the suite is an additional room with its own closet, offering flexibility as an office, extra bedroom, private gym, or a lavish dressing room. Located in a prestigious gated community in Lemoore, right on the golf course, this home enjoys close proximity to the freeway, placing convenience at your doorstep. Experience the best of Lemoore living--schedule your showing today and prepare to be enchanted.
